title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 14 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Sep 14 2022
description:
Betting markets favor Kari Lake to become AZ governor. KJP says Biden Regime is doing more to secure border than Trump did as record numbers of illegals cross into America. Vivek Ramaswamy, founder and executive chairman of Strive and author of the new book, Nation of Victims, joins Clay and Buck to discuss the backlash against wokeism. Joe Manchin rips Kamala Harris on the border. The only way Manchin can save his career is to become a Republican.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
